&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;echo &amp;#34;https://github.com/vicalloy/outline-docker-compose.git&amp;#34;&amp;gt;/myfile/outline/README_outline-docker-compose.md
